<h1>Snapshot</h1>
<p>With snapshot feature, you can download an html version of this conversation page.
You can use it as a template for automation marketing tools like mautic and mailchimp.</p>

<span>Select a marketing tool to generate a compatible snapshot</span>
<select id="" name="">
	<option value="mautic">Mautic</option>
</select>
<form action="{{conversation.url("conversation:integrations")}}" method="post">
	<input type="hidden" name="csrfmiddlewaretoken" value="{{ csrf_token }}">
	<input type="submit" value="Download">
</form>
<p><a href="{{ conversation.get_absolute_url() }}" title="{{ _('Back to conversation') }}"
		class="lowercase bold text-brand">
	<i class="fa fa-chevron-left"></i>{% trans %}Back to conversation{% endtrans %}
</a></p>
